title.rendered: PM2.5 filter activated carbon five-layer Protective replacement filter, 1,000/Pk

content.rendered:
General Information

Features:

 

  • Filtration technology: made of activated carbon and non-woven melt-blown filter cloth, five-layer filter system effectively keep away from PM 2.5 and a range of airborne contaminants (Please Note That The Mask Face Is Not a Filter)
  • Reasonable size: filters size measures approx. 12.5 x 8 cm/ 4.9 x 3.1 inches, compatible with most dust masks, easy to insert or replace the original one with no problem
  • Good design: multiple protection to isolate dust, multi-layer folding, good ventilation, double your protection against nasty substances, gases and odours with an additional filter inserted into the inside of your pollution mask
  • Wide applications: mouth mask filter anti airborne particles dust, seasonal allergies, smoke, pollution, ash, gardening pollen and so on, suit to most occasions.

excerpt.rendered: The PM2.5 filter activated carbon five-layer Protective replacement filter is a must-have essential to creating fresh air for reusable mask users, where it can lengthen the lifetime of washable masks for breathing. The PM2.5 Activated Carbon mask filter consists of five-layer filter material, effectively prevent pollutant like dust, small particle, PM2.5, fog from entering, ideal for protecting a users mouth and face from Dust, Haze, Germs, Allergies, Smoke, Pollution, Ash, Pollen, Gardening, Crafts.
